name: Homemade Oreo Cookies
description:
You will receive one dozen fresh baked homemade oreo cookies. I use high quality ingredients: real butter, fresh eggs, chocolate, ground flour, and high quality real vanilla. I have been told by many that these are the best homemade oreo cookies. These are a favorite of many!

The cookies will be made within 24 hours of your order and will ship the same day. Your cookies will come wrapped to keep freshness.

Need more then a dozen? Just contact me and I can set up a custom order for you.

All orders ship on Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday so that they arrive to you at their best.

If you live in the Yardley area, I can bake and deliver Monday through Friday. Shipping costs will be refunded.

Thanks for looking.
